Bounty Hunter
The Bounty Hunter pursues criminals and fugitives for profit. Part detective,
part warrior, they combine combat ability with surveillance, interrogation,
and tracking skills that make them relentless pursuers.

Bounty Hunters begin with a strong espionage and investigation skill set
alongside solid weapons training. They choose from Espionage, Military,
Rogue, and Technical categories.

Attribute requirements: PS 9, PE 9.
Starting equipment: Body armour, restraints, laser pistol, rifle, tracking
equipment, and a current bounty list.
